        {
            "title": "Dividend Payments ex-date of Coop Pank AS ",
            "id": "4528c06c-a0b0-45f4-b5a8-6294b8f1dd2d",
            "description": "In the year 2025, Coop Pank AS will be paying a dividend of 6.5 eurocents per share to its shareholders. The list of eligible shareholders for the dividend will be finalized on 22.04.2026 COB in the settlement system. The ex-date, marking the day when rights related to the shares change, is set for 21.04.2026. Starting from this date, individuals acquiring shares will not be entitled to receive the dividend for the 2025 financial year. The dividend will be distributed to shareholders on 27.04.2026.",
